{"word":"ἀγρότερος","slug":"ἀγρότερος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγρότερος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄγρα'><el>ἄγρα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> for <el>ἄγριος</el>, <i>wild</i>, of animals,<a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of <i>countrymen</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b>of plants, <i>wild</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>fond of the chase</i>; <el>Ἀγροτέρα</el>, <i>the Huntress</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> Artemis, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}